    "status" : "extensions",
    "div" : "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h2 id=\"title\">臺灣流感抗病毒藥劑-伺服端(TWIAM Server)</h2><ul><li>實作指引版本：1.0.0</li><li>FHIR版本：4.0.1</li><li>支援格式：<code>json</code></li><li>發佈日：2024-06-06</li><li>發佈者：衛福部疾病管制署</li></ul><h3 id=\"shallIGs\">必須（SHALL）支援以下實作指引</h3><ul><li><a href=\"index.html\">臺灣流感抗病毒藥劑實作指引(TWIAM IG)</a></li></ul><h2 id=\"rest\">Server的FHIR RESTful功能要求</h2><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h3 id=\"mode1\" class=\"panel-title\">模式：<code>server</code></h3></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div><p>臺灣流感抗病毒藥劑-伺服端(TWIAM Server)<b>必須(SHALL)</b>：<br/>(1)支援本實作指引中所有profiles<br/>(2)根據FHIR規範實作RESTful<br/>(3)回傳狀態碼<br/>\u00a0\u00a0 ①(Status 400)：無效參數(invalid parameter)<br/>\u00a0\u00a0 ②(Status 401/4xx)：未經授權的請求(unauthorized request)<br/>\u00a0\u00a0 ③(Status 403)：未充分授權的資料存取範圍(insufficient premission scope)<br/>\u00a0\u00a0 ④(Status 404)：未知的resource(unknown resource)<br/>(4)支援JSON格式<br/>(5)可識別每個新增到Server的實例(instance)之meta.profile是否為臺灣流感抗病毒藥劑Profiles Defining URL，並確認實例是否依循Profile製作。</p><p>臺灣流感抗病毒藥劑-伺服端<b>建議應該(SHOULD)</b>：<br/>(1)支援XML格式。</p></div></div></div><h3 id=\"resourcesCap1\">Resources或Profiles的RESTful功能</h3><h4 id=\"resourcesSummary1\">Summary</h4><p>共有十類Resources支援查詢，查詢參數如表列：</p><div class=\"table-responsive\"><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th><b>Resource型別</b></th><th><b>Profile</b></th><th><b>支援的Profiles</b></th><th>Create</th><th>Update</th><th>Read</th><th>Delete</th><th><b>支援的查詢參數</b></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"#Bundle1-1\">Bundle</a></td><td>-</td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-bundle-reporting-twiam.html\">合約院所上傳使用回報資料-Bundle Reporting TWIAM</a><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-bundle-response-twiam.html\">回報資料上傳結果-Bundle Response TWIAM</a></td><td>y</td><td>y</td><td>y</td><td>-</td><td>timestamp + message.sender:Organization.identifier,<br/>timestamp + message.sender:Organization.identifier + message.focus:Patient.name,<br/>timestamp + message.sender:Organization.identifier + message.focus:Patient.identifier,<br/>timestamp + message.sender:Organization.identifier + message.focus:Patient.name + message.focus:Patient.identifier,<br/>message.sender:Organization.identifier + _id</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#MessageHeader1-2\">MessageHeader</a></td><td>-</td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-messageheader-reporting-twiam.html\">合約院所上傳使用回報資料訊息-MessageHeader Reporting TWIAM</a><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-messageheader-response-twiam.html\">回報資料上傳結果訊息-MessageHeader Response TWIAM</a></td><td>y</td><td>y</td><td>y</td><td>-</td><td>focus, sender</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#OperationOutcome1-3\">OperationOutcome</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-operationoutcome-twiam.html\">系統回應訊息-OperationOutcome TWIAM</a></td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#MedicationAdministration1-4\">MedicationAdministration</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-medicationadministration-twiam.html\">給藥-MedicationAdministration TWIAM</a></td><td>-</td><td>y</td><td>y</td><td>y</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Medication1-5\">Medication</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-medication-twiam.html\">物資品項-Medication TWIAM</a></td><td>-</td><td>y</td><td>y</td><td>y</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Patient1-6\">Patient</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-patient-twiam.html\">投藥者資料-Patient TWIAM</a></td><td>-</td><td>y</td><td>y</td><td>y</td><td>-</td><td>identifier, name</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Group1-7\">Group</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-group-twiam.html\">群體-Group TWIAM</a></td><td>-</td><td>y</td><td>y</td><td>y</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Organization1-8\">Organization</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-organization-group-twiam.html\">群聚事件單位-Organization Group TWIAM</a></td><td><a href=\"https://twcore.mohw.gov.tw/ig/twcore/0.2.2/StructureDefinition-Organization-hosp-twcore.html\">TW Core Organization Hospital Department</a></td><td>y</td><td>y</td><td>y</td><td>-</td><td>identifier</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Observation1-9\">Observation</a></td><td>-</td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-observation-bodyheight-twiam.html\">身高-Observation Body Height TWIAM</a><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-observation-bodyweight-twiam.html\">體重(Observation Body Weight WIAM)</a><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-observation-major-illness-twiam.html\">重大傷病-Observation Major Illness TWIAM</a><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-observation-immunodeficiency-twiam.html\">免疫不全-Observation Immunodeficiency TWIAM</a></td><td>y</td><td>y</td><td>y</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Condition1-10\">Condition</a></td><td>-</td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-condition-chronic-illness-twiam.html\">慢性病-Condition Chronic Illness TWIAM</a><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-condition-diagnosis-twiam.html\">診斷或診斷碼-Condition Diagnosis TWIAM</a></td><td>y</td><td>y</td><td>y</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr></tbody></table></div><hr/><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"Bundle1-1\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">預期的遵從度： 必須（SHALL）</span>Bundle</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Core FHIR Resource</span><br/><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/bundle.html\">Bundle</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\"><span class=\"lead\">支援的參照政策（Reference policy）</span><br/><code>resolves</code></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">能力摘要</span><br/><ul><li><strong>必須（SHALL）</strong>支援 <code>create</code>, <code>update</code>, <code>read</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-6\"><span class=\"lead\">支援的Profiles</span><p><a href=\"StructureDefinition-bundle-reporting-twiam.html\">合約院所上傳使用回報資料-Bundle Reporting TWIAM</a><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-bundle-response-twiam.html\">回報資料上傳結果-Bundle Response TWIAM</a></p></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-12\"><span class=\"lead\">Search Parameters</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>遵從度</th><th>參數</th><th>類型</th><th>範例</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>必須（SHALL）</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-Bundle-timestamp.html\">timestamp</a> + <a href=\"SearchParameter-Bundle-message.html\">message</a>.<a href=\"SearchParameter-MessageHeader-sender.html\">sender</a>:<a href=\"SearchParameter-Organization-identifier.html\">Organization.identifier</a></td><td><code>date</code>, <code>reference</code>, <code>token</code></td><td><code>GET [base]/Bundle?timestamp={gt|lt|ge|le}[date]&amp;message.sender:Organization.identifier=[code]</code></td></tr><tr><td><b>建議應該（SHOULD）</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-Bundle-timestamp.html\">timestamp</a> + <a href=\"SearchParameter-Bundle-message.html\">message</a>.<a href=\"SearchParameter-MessageHeader-sender.html\">sender</a>:<a href=\"SearchParameter-Organization-identifier.html\">Organization.identifier</a> + <a href=\"SearchParameter-Bundle-message.html\">message</a>.<a href=\"SearchParameter-MessageHeader-focus.html\">focus</a>:<a href=\"SearchParameter-Patient-name.html\">Patient.name</a></td><td><code>date</code>, <code>reference</code>, <code>token</code>, <code>string</code></td><td><code>GET [base]/Bundle?timestamp={gt|lt|ge|le}[date]&amp;message.sender:Organization.identifier=[code]&amp;message.focus:Patient.name=[name]</code></td></tr><tr><td><b>建議應該（SHOULD）</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-Bundle-timestamp.html\">timestamp</a> + <a href=\"SearchParameter-Bundle-message.html\">message</a>.<a href=\"SearchParameter-MessageHeader-sender.html\">sender</a>:<a href=\"SearchParameter-Organization-identifier.html\">Organization.identifier</a> + <a href=\"SearchParameter-Bundle-message.html\">message</a>.<a href=\"SearchParameter-MessageHeader-focus.html\">focus</a>:<a href=\"SearchParameter-Patient-identifier.html\">Patient.identifier</a></td><td><code>date</code>, <code>reference</code>, <code>token</code></td><td><code>GET [base]/Bundle?timestamp={gt|lt|ge|le}[date]&amp;message.sender:Organization.identifier=[code]&amp;message.focus:Patient.identifier=[code]</code></td></tr><tr><td><b>建議應該（SHOULD）</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-Bundle-timestamp.html\">timestamp</a> + <a href=\"SearchParameter-Bundle-message.html\">message</a>.<a href=\"SearchParameter-MessageHeader-sender.html\">sender</a>:<a href=\"SearchParameter-Organization-identifier.html\">Organization.identifier</a> + <a href=\"SearchParameter-Bundle-message.html\">message</a>.<a href=\"SearchParameter-MessageHeader-focus.html\">focus</a>:<a href=\"SearchParameter-Patient-name.html\">Patient.name</a> + <a href=\"SearchParameter-Bundle-message.html\">message</a>.<a href=\"SearchParameter-MessageHeader-focus.html\">focus</a>:<a href=\"SearchParameter-Patient-identifier.html\">Patient.identifier</a></td><td><code>date</code>, <code>reference</code>, <code>token</code>, <code>string</code></td><td><code>GET [base]/Bundle?timestamp={gt|lt|ge|le}[date]&amp;message.sender:Organization.identifier=[code]&amp;message.focus:Patient.name=[name]&amp;message.focus:Patient.identifier=[code]</code></td></tr><tr><td><b>建議應該（SHOULD）</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-Bundle-message.html\">message</a>.<a href=\"SearchParameter-MessageHeader-sender.html\">sender</a>:<a href=\"SearchParameter-Organization-identifier.html\">Organization.identifier</a> + <a href=\"SearchParameter-Bundle-message.html\">message</a>.<a href=\"SearchParameter-MessageHeader-sender.html\">sender</a>:<a href=\"SearchParameter-Bundle-id.html\">_id</a></td><td><code>reference</code>, <code>token</code></td><td><code>GET [base]/Bundle?message.sender:Organization.identifier=[code]&amp;_id=[id]</code></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\">\u00a0</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"MessageHeader1-2\" clas